Z = X + Y
f_Z(z) = \int_{-\infty}^{+\infty} f(z - y)g(y)dy
 = \int_{0}^{z} \lambda e^{-\lambda(z - y)}\lambda e^{-\lambda y}dy
 = \int_{0}^{z} \lambda^2 e^{-\lambda z}dy
 = \lambda^2 z e^{-\lambda z}
